---
title: Shawarma-Inspired Turkey Meatballs with Roasted Veggie Couscous and Feta Cheese
description: This deconstructed wrap is inspired by the classic Middle Eastern dish! With savoury turkey meatballs, roasted veggies, couscous and salty feta cheese, it's equally as tasty and colourful as the iconic handheld.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/boulettes-de-dinde-style-shawarma-0f592d3b.jpg
